::Battera::

Feels real stupid for not watching where she was going. "Ouch." 
rubbing her head. She looks up at WindRider. Her face turns a deep 
red.  "I'm fine. No wonder bats are blind. I didn't even see that 
coming."  She took his hand and stood up. "Sorry for spoiling the 
race."  she looked down.  Then an idea popped into her head.  She 
transformed into bot mode. She tapped him on the shoulder. "TAG! Your 
it!" and ran for the hatch.
